lyrics:
(Verse 1)
Writers of history,
Stand by my side,
Look into my eyes and see
People walk, but never part.

Someone stole the moon tonight,
Took away my light,
Everything is black and white,
Who’s the fool who told you,
That boys don’t cry?

(Pre-Chorus)
Hours and more hours, and flowers,
Life is no game for the fearful,
Why does time go mad?
style: Eurovision power ballad, emotional and sad, slow, starts with piano, female voice, piano and violins
